When I deleted ["GetAnySDFValue"](#!/osrf/gazebo/commits/c867a38#Lgazebo/physics/PresetManager.ccF59) in the last commit, I got rid of a conversion from `sdf::Vector3` to `math::Vector3`:

```
else if (typeid(sdf::Vector3) == _elem->GetValue()->GetType())
{
   ret = _elem->Get<gazebo::math::Vector3>();
}
```

I believe `Element::Get` is able to convert the `SDF::Vector3` object to a `math::Vector3` because of the `lexical_cast` done in [Param.hh of SDF](https://bitbucket.org/osrf/sdformat/src/56d0489bf4340224cacaa56656ce5c1308de2cc9/include/sdf/Param.hh?at=default#cl-146).

I did, and I got this error:

